  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast at Villa La Gardenia &amp; Oleandra is buffet style with hot and cold options including freshly baked breads, pastries and fruit fresh from the garden.</p>
<p>Guests can also have lunch at the hotel's a la carte restaurant (payable locally).</p>
<p>Dinner is a choice of four courses and a small salad buffet. The hotel offers fresh, Italian cuisine and uses home-grown produce to create traditional dishes.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
