  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Gardenia Comfort Rooms</strong> are around 20m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They have a balcony with lake views.</p>
<p><strong>Oleandra Superior Rooms</strong> are around 30m² and can sleep up to two people. They have a terrace with lake views.</p>
<p><strong>Gardenia Luxury Rooms</strong> are 35m² and sleep up to three people. They have recently been refurbished and have a contemporary style and a balcony with lake views.</p>
<p><strong>Gardenia Single Rooms </strong>are about 20m² and have a balcony with side lake views.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Shower stall</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Pool towel &amp; slippers</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request.</p>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A tourist tax of approx. €2 per person (aged 14+) per day is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
